            "description": "<p>We are software development company. We design, create, provision and maintain our own products and web solutions for our clients.</p><h3>Responsibilities</h3><ul><li>Technically contributing to medium to large-scale projects, resolving issues and researching to determine a solution</li><li>Troubleshooting problems of a complex nature</li><li>Create UI and UX from proposed designs, reviewing them with the PO and designers</li><li>Keep abreast of new browser capabilities and new web design paradigms</li><li>Building integrations to third party technologies</li></ul><h3>Technologies we use</h3><ul><li>JavaScript (Angular, jQuery)</li><li>Python</li><li>MySQL, Neo4j</li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li>HTML5/CSS3</li><li>JavaScript, jQuery</li><li>Git</li><li>understanding of OOP and MVC</li></ul><h3>Desirable</h3><ul><li>JS frameworks: Angular, Backbone, Ember, React, etc.</li><li>CSS frameworks: Bootstrap, Foundation</li><li>CSS pre-processors such as Less or SASS</li><li>JS Unit testing</li><li>ES6</li><li>Gulp/Grunt/Webpack\u200b\u200b</li></ul><h3>And most important</h3><p>\u0406 \u0449\u0435!!! \u041b\u044e\u0431\u0438\u0442\u0438 \u0441\u0432\u043e\u044e \u0440\u043e\u0431\u043e\u0442\u0443 \u0442\u0430 \u0432\u043c\u0456\u0442\u0438 \u0441\u043f\u0456\u043b\u043a\u0443\u0432\u0430\u0442\u0438\u0441\u044f \u0437\u0456 \u0441\u0432\u043e\u0457\u043c\u0438 \u043a\u043e\u043b\u0435\u0433\u0430\u043c\u0438 \u0437\u0430\u0440\u0430\u0434\u0438 \u0434\u043e\u0441\u044f\u0433\u043d\u0435\u043d\u043d\u044f \u044f\u043a\u0456\u0441\u043d\u043e\u0433\u043e \u0440\u0435\u0437\u0443\u043b\u044c\u0442\u0430\u0442\u0443 \u043c\u0430\u0441\u0442 \u0445\u0435\u0432!</p>",
