            "created": "2015-03-26 15:13:42",
            "description": "<p>LivaRava development team worked smart for you to make your neuroning experience even better. Now it is so easy and simple as a piece of cake. Even a kid can do it!</p>\r\n<p>So, we have noticed that an old form was not good enough and we decided to improve it significantly.</p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Neuroning form was significantly improved!\" src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rtEwIbj.jpg\" alt=\"Neuroning Form\"></p><p>All you need to do now is:</p>\r\n<ul><li>Start searching something, afterwards to press the \"Neuron it!\" button.</li><li>You will get a popup window, where you can input text, link or upload image.</li><li>Everything else will be done for you by LivaRava.</li><li>The data will be parsed and indexed automatically.</li><li>In the end just press the \"Create axon\" button to build a new association to the current neuron.</li><li>That's it!</li></ul>\r\n<p>Everyday we are working smart and hard to build the best knowledge management tool for you!</p><p>Sincerely,<br>LivaRava Team</p><hr>\r\n<p>We are waiting for you at our exhibition stand at Collision Conference in Las Vegas, Nevada, USA on May 5, 2015. It will be a great pleasure for us to have a small chat with you in person. We will show you the advantages of LivaRava, its endless possibilities and how to smooth your experience with the service. See you soon!</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>We continue to send invitations for LivaRava to our community fans. If you are interested in beta-testing of our innovative web-service please do not hesitate to ask us about it. Write a short letter with the request for invitation to <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"mailto:support@livarava.com\">support@livarava.com</a>. You will get $10, 3 neuron subscription and 3GB of disk space.</p>",
