            "created": "2015-03-06 11:31:52",
            "description": "<p></p><p></p><p>LivaRava 5.1 is here! This release has been about improvements that helps users to make their first steps in LivaRava. We have had 210 commits since last release. Woohoo!</p><p>Here are some of the highlights:</p><ul><li>Simplified neuroning form that makes creation of new axon even easier</li><li>Created <a href=\"http://www.livarava.com/neuron/12908/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">introduction video</a> that shortly describes the fundamentals of LivaRava for new users</li><li>Created <a href=\"http://www.livarava.com/neuron/13139/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">tutorial video</a> that describes first steps and main functionality of LivaRava</li><li>Added First Step page that gives an opportunity for new users to choose first neurons for browsing and neuroning</li><li>Added language selection on homepage</li><li>Added new interface and localization language - Russian</li><li>Fixed a lot of known bugs</li></ul><h3>New team member</h3><p>We are stoked to welcome <a href=\"http://www.livarava.com/member/12268/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Artem</a>\r\n to the LivaRava team! Artem brings with him good graphics design skills to LivaRava\u2019s team. You can already enjoy his work in <a href=\"http://www.livarava.com/neuron/13139/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">new tutorial video</a>.</p><h3>We are going to Las Vegas!</h3><p>Yes! We are going to <a href=\"http://www.livarava.com/neuron/Las Vegas/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Las Vegas</a> to <a href=\"http://www.livarava.com/neuron/Collision Conference/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Collision Conference</a>. No way back! See you there.<br></p><p>With respect and love,<br><a href=\"http://www.livarava.com/member/1/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Artem Kariavka</a> and<br>LivaRava development team</p>",
